pros:
The company has a very clear culture & vision;
Excellent teammates;
Benefits and salary are ok;

I worked as seasonal part-time specialist and while it was hard to manage 2 jobs (I had a full time at the moment too), my team at Apple still made it an unforgettable experience! It's amazing how diverse and inclusive the company is. Being from a different country I felt very welcoming and understood. 
Some of the pros: 
- competitive hourly pay;
- flexible hours; 
- employee discount;
- fun and very positive environment!

cons:
Very challenging work environment within supply chain; 
Products intro schedule are pretty tight ;
Diplomatic environment;
Work life balance can be improved;
Advice to Management
Create a work life balance environment can make staff more creative;
